## Integration

**Run when**:
- After implementing a feature (quick pass)
- Before performance-sensitive releases
- Part of periodic codebase health checks

**Triggers**:
- `::sdc-audit` command
- "Find set/dict/comprehension opportunities"
- "Data structure substitution audit"

